menu "Sensor Manager"

config SENSOR_MANAGER_PUBLISH_INTERVAL_MS
    int "Sensor telemetry publish interval (ms)"
    default 2000
    range 1000 600000
    help
        Interval at which the sensor manager aggregates registered sensor readings
        and publishes a telemetry payload via MQTT for app monitoring.
        Default is 2000ms (2 seconds) for responsive app updates.
        Minimum: 1000ms (1 second), Maximum: 600000ms (10 minutes).

endmenu

